        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "> why should we change it?\n\nA dialog doesn't have to be shown. In any case, the current behavior is that \"the buffer will be loaded anyway,\" but the read error indicator is shown, an error is thrown in Lua, and a large and intrusive message is unavoidably printed.\n\n> If you want the swap dialog\n\nI don't want the swap dialog, I want to programmatically handle the existence of the swap file in a sane manner. ",
